Package: fflr
Title: Collect ESPN Fantasy Football Data
Version: 1.9.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Kiernan",
           family = "Nicholls",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "kiernann@protonmail.com")
Description: Format the raw data from the ESPN fantasy football API
    <https://fantasy.espn.com/apis/v3/games/ffl/> into tidy tables.
    Scrape data on public leagues, rosters, athletes, and matches.
